<p>Online banking is built to support a wide range of computers and mobile devices. Minimum requirements to use online banking include:</p>
<ul>
<li>For desktop computers, Microsoft Windows 10 or Mac OS X 10.10 with a supported PC or Mac®.</li>
<li>Supported browsers for desktop computers include the current and previous two versions of Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, Microsoft Edge and Safari.</li>
<li>The mobile app requires Android 14x and later or iOS 16.x and later.</li>
<li>Fingerprint login is only supported on eligible Android devices. Touch Authentication is only available on eligible Apple iOS devices.</li>
<li>Remote deposit requires a mobile device with a rear-facing camera with a 5 megapixel or higher resolution.</li>
</ul>

System and browser requirements
Online banking is built to support a wide range of computers and mobile
devices. Minimum requirements to use online banking include:
For desktop computers, Microsoft Windows 10 or Mac OS X 10.10 with
a supported PC or Mac®.
Supported browsers for desktop computers include the current and
previous two versions of Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, Microsoft
Edge and Safari.
The mobile app requires Android 14x and later or iOS 16.x and later.
Fingerprint login is only supported on eligible Android devices. Touch
Authentication is only available on eligible Apple iOS devices.
Remote deposit requires a mobile device with a rear-facing camera
with a 5 megapixel or higher resolution.
Online banking terms and agreements
Download and review the latest terms and agreements for online banking.

System and browser requirements
Online banking is built to support a wide range of computers and mobile
devices. Minimum requirements to use online banking include:
For desktop computers, Microsoft Windows 10 or Mac OS X 10.10 with
a supported PC or Mac®.
Supported browsers for desktop computers include the current and
previous two versions of Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, Microsoft
Edge and Safari.
The mobile app requires Android 14x and later or iOS 16.x and later.
Fingerprint login is only supported on eligible Android devices. Touch
Authentication is only available on eligible Apple iOS devices.
Remote deposit requires a mobile device with a rear-facing camera
with a 5 megapixel or higher resolution.
